---
title: Easy Sichuan Chicken Tacos & Soy Slaw with Crushed Peanuts
description: Save time at dinner and still end up with a tasty spread of delicious flavours! Tender chicken in a mild Sichuan paste gets
loaded into these fun tacos, along with a creamy slaw and crunchy peanuts. You're in for a family feast!
